Spotify creates a year-end playlist of my most-played songs for the previous year, and revisiting what I listened to awhile ago was fun and edifying for me.
In 2016, I was young and falling in love with Katie and our lives in Michigan&hellip;
Later, I grew more confident and listened to music that was spunky and energetic - maybe I was too, you decide&hellip;
2019 and 2020 were different. They were hard.
